  "textPreview": "Free June 9 event: How to win brand visibility when AI decides what gets seen →\nSolutions\nTools\nResources\nPricing\nEN\nSign in\nTalk to an expert\nStart free trial\nSEO MCP: Use SE Ranking’s live data inside any AI assistant\n\nPut 180+ SEO and GEO tools behind every prompt: keyword data, backlinks, domain insights, audits, AI search visibility, and more — all inside your favorite AI assistant.\n\nSign up\nSetup guide\n\nNo credit card required\n\nSE Ranking MCP use cases for everyday workflows\n\nLet your AI assistant reason, compare, and analyze with live SE Ranking data behind every answer.\n\nKEYWORD RESEARCH\nFind keyword ideas worth targeting\n\nDiscover high-potential keyword ideas for your niche, then compare them by demand and recent trends to choose the best content angles.\n\nExample prompt:\n“Find 50 keyword ideas for [seed keyword] in [country], including related, similar, long-tail, and question-based keywords. Show search volume, CPC, competition, difficulty, and 6-month trend data. Group them by intent and highlight the top 10 opportunities for new content.”\n\nDOMAIN ANALYSIS\nSpot recent changes in any domain’s search performance\n\nGet a quick view of organic and paid visibility, then dig into the keyword movements behind the biggest traffic gains and losses.\n\nExample prompt:\n“Analyze recent search performance for [domain] in [country] over the last 30 days. Show organic and paid visibility, top 20 traffic-driving keywords, 10 strongest gains, 10 sharpest drops, ranking URLs, and estimated traffic impact.”\n\nAI SEARCH\nBuild a competitor AI search report\n\nSee how your domain and competitors show up in AI answers, which brands are cited most often, and which topics your site is missing from.\n\nExample prompt:\n“Compare AI search visibility for [target domain] and [competitor domain] in [country] across ChatGPT and Gemini. Create a visibility leaderboard and heatmap. For each brand, pull 20 prompts: 10 brand mentions and 10 source citations. Show who leads, which topics each brand ",
